sourcesContent: import React,{ Component } from "react"; import { Card, CardBody, CardHeader, Label, Input, FormGroup, CardFooter, Button,Col } from 'reactstrap'; const initialValues = { budget: '', programId: '', subFundingSourceId: '', budgetAmt: '', startDate: '', stopDate: '', // programList: [], // subFundingSourceList: [] } export default class AddProgram extends Component{ constructor(props){ super(props); this.state={ program:{ label:{ label_en:'' }, realm:{ realmId:'' }, realmCountry:{ realmCountryId:'' }, organisation:{ organisationId:'' }, programManager:{ programManagerUserId:'' }, airFreightPercentage:'', seaFreightPercentage:'', deliveredToRecivedLeadTime:'', draftToSubmittedLeadTime:'', planDraftLeadTime:'', submittedToApprovedLeadTime:'', approvedToShippedLeadTime:'', monthInFutureForAmc:'', monthInPastForAmc:'', healthAreaId:'', programNotes:'' } } this.dataChange=this.dataChange.bind(this); } dataChange(){ } render() { return ( Add Program ); } }
